# Benefits

## Of React

* Components allow to break down UI logic into small, reusable and maintainable pieces of code
* useState allows managing of application state - React takes over rerendering
* useEffect for loading data initially or when something changed
* React Router https://reactrouter.com/en/main allows creation of Single Page Application (no page reload)

## Of Next.js

* Everything from React
* Conventions for routing, data fetching, etc.
* Server side rendering
